  "_id": "sddUehP0SDWmfW86",
  "img": "icons/dice/d10black.svg",
  "description": "<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 8\"><div class=\"layoutArea\"><div class=\"column\"><p><span style=\"font-family:'CIDFont+F1'\">For your Orbital/Deep Space Settlement, Roll d50 and pick 1-2 entries from the relevant column in the Oracle. A population of “Hundreds and above” are “Medium-Large”. The results are what you first hear or smell.<br /><br />If you roll “PA System” for a “Primitive”, “Backwater”, “Dilapidated” or “Over-Crowded” Settlement, you can ignore a result of “PA System” and re-roll on the Senses Oracle.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:'CIDFont+F1'\">In a “Defended” Settlement, the PA System will be barking out military order.<br />In a “High-Tech” Settlement, the PA System will be running ads for high-tech goods.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:'CIDFont+F1'\">In a “Military-Industrial” Settlement, the PA System will be running ads for locally-manufactured military hardware.</span></p></div></div></div>",
